http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/BJP-criticises-Pawan%E2%80%99s-remarks-on-Venkaiah/article14636402.ece

City BJP has condemned the criticism on BJP and its top leader M. Venkaiah Naidu by actor and Jana Sena founder Pawan Kalyan. His speech at Kakinada exposed the lack of knowledge on the difference between special package and Special Category Status and the recommendations of the 14{+t}{+h}Finance Commission and youth from Andhra being denied jobs leading to separate Andhra agitation of which Mr. Venkaiah Naidu was a leader, city BJP president M. Nagendra told reporters.The party took exception to the language used, particularly “stabbing by BJP” and expressed the doubt whether the hand of Congress or YSRC was behind it.